definition.value: A butan-4-olide having a methylene group at the 3-position and two methyl substituents at the 5-position.
A CDP-diacylglycerol in which the acyl groups at positions 1 and 2 are specified as tetradec-7-enoyl.
A dihydroxy-1,3,5-triazine that is 1,3,5-triazine-2,4-diol substituted by a chloro group at position 6.
